    "These forecasts present a range of possible outcomes with associated probabilities, offering a more nuanced understanding of long-term risks.",
    "In addition, there has been a trade-off between the spatial resolution of predictions and the time scale over which they are madelonger time scales typically meant broader, less detailed spatial predictions (Fig. 4).",
